                                Anatomy of a Phishing Email: Unmasking the Threat
                            </h6>
                            <p class="card-text text-secondary fw-light mb-2" style="white-space: normal; line-height: 1;">
								<small>  Anatomy of a Phishing Email: Unmasking the Threat</small>
							</p>
                        </div>
                        <a asp-action="PhishingEmailArticle" asp-controller="Blogs" class="text-primary text-decoration-none mt-auto">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Article 7 -->
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card h-100 articleCard rounded-4">
                    <img src="~/Images/blog8.jpg" class=" rounded-top-4" alt="Malicious Link Graphic">
                    <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                        <div class="flex-grow-1">
                            <h6 class="card-title  mb-2" style="display: -webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp: 2; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; overflow: hidden;">
                                What is a Malicious Link? A Comprehensive Guide
                            </h6>
                            <p class="card-text text-secondary fw-light mb-2" style="white-space: normal; line-height: 1;">
								<small>What is a Malicious Link? A Comprehensive Guide</small>
							</p>
                        </div>
                        <a asp-action="MaliciousLinkArticle" asp-controller="Blogs" class="text-primary text-decoration-none mt-auto">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
